<MELItem itemNbr="21-31-06" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-31-06.1.2-21-31-06">
<Title>Cabin Differential Pressure Indication</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Cabin Altitude Indication Operates Normally</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Cabin altitude indication operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>A chart is provided to convert cabin altitude to cabin differential pressure.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Cabin differential pressure may be derived from the following chart using indicated values of airplane altitude and cabin altitude.</Para>
<GraphicSet id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.GR.2-21-31-06.712524.2-21-31-06">
<Illustration fileRef="G2-21-31-06.fm_712527" linkRef="URN:X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.NX.GR.2-21-31-06.712527." />
</GraphicSet>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Unpressurized Flight</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Flight is conducted unpressurized.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Cargo compartments remain empty or contain only non flammable/combustible ballast, empty cargo handling equipment (ballast may be loaded in ULDs), or fly away kits (excluding items such as cans of hydraulic fluid, cleaning solvents, batteries, capacitors, chemical generators, etc).</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Establish airplane in unpressurized flight configuration (AMM DDG 21-31-06).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Use MEL item 21-31-01B (M) procedure.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Use MEL item 21-31-01B (O) procedure.</Para>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
